#
# These Kubernetes RBAC findings are expected for this operator and are documented
# inline in the rendered manifests. The Helm security job still fails on any
# unignored MEDIUM/HIGH/CRITICAL finding.

# RoleDefinition discovery must list API resources across groups so generated
# Role/ClusterRole output stays accurate.
KSV-0046

# BindDefinition intentionally manages RoleBindings/ClusterRoleBindings and the
# generated roles they reference.
KSV-0050

# The webhook server certificate controller must patch admission webhook
# configurations with its CA bundle.
KSV-0114

# The webhook certificate controller needs namespace-scoped Secret list/watch
# for its informer/cache; get/patch/update remain resourceName-scoped to the
# operator TLS Secret.
KSV-0113

# The chart defaults to GHCR, which is the project's release registry. Trivy's
# generic trusted-registry rule does not know project-specific registry policy.
KSV-0125
